Class Summary
AutomaticConduit will automatically create a filter chain from a list of filter names
e.g.
BasicConduit unidirectional pipe the writable end of a conduit is its "entrance" (AKA drain or sink) the readable end of a conduit is its "exit" (AKA source)
ConduitArgs helps with args for a conduit
VoidConduit this is a placeholder conduit which does not pass any data.
